abstract: LAST REQUEST or BENTON.--When the dying veteran was within a few hours of his end, he addressed a letter to Gen. HOUSTON and the Hon. GEO. JONES, requesting that Congress would take no notice of his impending death. abstract: There are prevaient misapprehensions respecting the recent treaty with Nicaragua While it is assumed by some to be a Protectorate of that Republic, others aver that it is nothing less than virtual annexation. The treaty is neither the one nor the other. It does not in the least disturb the nationality of Nicaragua, and it is a Protectorate of the Transit route simply,--not of the country through whose territory that route passes.
